OL,4,CMy decade of internet rape and death
OL,5,Cthreats - Lauren Mayberry
OL,6,GLauren Mayberry was 27 when she was
OL,7,Gsent rape threats after wearing a
OL,8,Gblack mini dress in a music video.
OL,10,FThe frontwoman of synth pop band
OL,11,FChvrches had become the target of a
OL,12,Ftorrent of online abuse, following the
OL,13,Frelease of the track Leave a Trace
OL,14,Ffrom the band's acclaimed second album.
OL,16,FOne person offered to hand her a gun,
OL,17,Fif she couldn't deal with the backlash.
OL,19,FShe decided to respond in an interview
OL,20,Fwith Channel 4's Cathy Newman, in
OL,21,Fwhich she branded the abuse
OL,22,F"ludicrous".
